api_list.name: Amazon Search
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://amazon-scrapper-pro.p.rapidapi.com/search/{searchquery}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "amazon-scrapper-pro.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

body.name: CHUWI CoreBook X Laptop 14'',Intel Core i3-10110U, Full HD (2160X1440) IPS Display, 8GB RAM 512GB SSD PC, Windows 10 Portable Notebook, WiFi 6/Backlit Keyboard/BT5.1/Type-C/PD 2.0 Fast Charge
body.product_category: Electronics › Computers & Accessories › Computers & Tablets › Laptops › Traditional Laptops
body.small_description:
About this item
 
【New Generation Intel CPU】Latest Intel Core i3-10110U processor (up to 4.1GHz) makes the CoreBook X gaming laptop ideal for a variety of complex offices and games. Equipped with 8GB DDR4 RAM and 512GB Kingston NVMe SSD, provides wider space and higher speeds for e-books, songs, videos, photos, and music. Comes with slots for DDR4 RAM, and supports memory upgrades for higher performance. 【 14-inch Full HD IPS display】2K resolution (2160x1440) shows stunning colors and clarity. 3:2 aspect ratio, IPS technology for wide viewing angles. This Windows 10 laptop is designed to relieve eye strain and vision fatigue, with Flicker-Free and Low Blue Light certifications from TUV Rheinland. This slim laptop has an integrated HD webcam with a microphone 【 Latest WiFi 6 & Bluetooth 5.1】The speed of WiFi 6 is almost 5X faster than WiFi 5. Intel Wireless-AC 7265 Wireless module supports 2.4G /5G dual-band and the top speed can reach 867Mbps, providing a more smooth Wireless network experience. Data transmission speed is +100% compared to Bluetooth 4.2, which makes the connection more stable and faster. 【 Long Battery life & Backlit Keyboard】46.2WH high-capacity lithium-ion battery and PD2.0 fast charging, 60% of the power in just one hour. The battery life of the music pc is up to 8 hours, which is enough for a whole day's use. The energy-efficient WLED backlight Keyboard enables comfortable and accurate typing, even in low light. 【 USB-C interface & Free Warranty】Windows laptop is equipped with the full-function USB-C interface, which supports audio, video, and data transmission. Many interfaces such as USB-A 3.0*1, 3.5mm headphone jack, M.2 SSD extension, Micro-SD, etc. CHUWI offers a free Warranty for 1 year. CONTACT US: Login your amazon account > choose "Your orders" > find the order > click "Contact seller".
